data.description: Discover the comfort of modern living in this better-than-new home boasting 4 bd and 2.5 baths. With attention to detail, this residence surpasses the standard, featuring upgraded amenities and contemporary finishes throughout including quartz countertops  & white cabinets in kitchen. AC is an added bonus. The bedrooms provide comfort and flexibility, with the convenience of a jack & jill bathroom. Seller's relocation out of state, presents a unique opportunity to make this exceptional property yours.
